snippet.title: How I Made A Top 100 Game Out Of 1k Games
snippet.description:
In this video i will talk about how i made my game A Strange Hotel for the Blackthornprod game jam. The jam was a lot of fun, hope you enjoy the video.

join the discord: https://discord.gg/6ebpsqtDYa

play this game: https://eminspace.itch.io/a-strange-hotel

follow me on twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/eminspace​

And remember, i am a she, lol.
